    "description": "此为 白日梦：被遗忘的悲伤 的第一幕，这是一款恐惧随行、谜题丰富，且氛围浓郁的冒险游戏。<br><br>白日梦：被遗忘的悲伤”是一款气氛浓郁的冒险游戏，讲述了男孩格里芬的感人故事，他不断与内心的恐惧斗争。幸运的是，他的泰迪熊朋友比利总是在那里帮助他。<br>旅程不会容易。走过无垠的黑暗和光明会将英雄的记忆变成新的感觉。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/6c1504a8db5d5fc8adb53100e60b212b.poster.avif?t=1691588001\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/6c1504a8db5d5fc8adb53100e60b212b.webm?t=1691588001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>比利的帮助非常宝贵。他可以被送到格里芬无法到达的地方：被抛过高高的木梁，被托付运行棘手的机制，或爬进一个小洞。齐心协力，这两者可以移动重物，克服陷阱，成功克服困难挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/6d36714faae84d8e191d0c81ccbf23f7.poster.avif?t=1691588001\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/6d36714faae84d8e191d0c81ccbf23f7.webm?t=1691588001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>发现感人的故事</strong></h2><br>你不会每天在一个未知的地方醒来，身边有一只活的泰迪熊。我们的孩子格里芬也不会。但他在那里，在一个有待解决的谜团的底部，在一个温馨故事的开始，有两个朋友等待被告知。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/53c031feecac97527076ffac8cc39039.poster.avif?t=1691588001\" width=616 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/53c031feecac97527076ffac8cc39039.webm?t=1691588001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>克服严峻挑战</strong></h2><br>用比利的帮助来解决错综复杂的谜题并探索世界。你可以直接控制格里芬，但你也可以拿起、投掷和给你的泰迪熊同伴发出命令，以帮助你的进展。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/e99e97f35431441d93759b80305b6acb.poster.avif?t=1691588001\" width=616 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/e99e97f35431441d93759b80305b6acb.webm?t=1691588001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索神秘世界</strong></h2><br>格里芬发现自己身处一个黑暗的地方，被过去的幻象所困扰，但这个世界不仅有厄运和阴郁。一旦你鼓起力量继续前进，你就会发现一个多姿多彩的迷人世界，充满浮动的城堡和崎岖的洞穴、童话般的森林和阳光明媚的平原。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/8462195a2bca4dff923f60b69c339409.poster.avif?t=1691588001\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2247560/extras/8462195a2bca4dff923f60b69c339409.webm?t=1691588001\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
